features: 🦕【DIY TAKE APART DINOSAUR TOYS】Kids can assemble dinosaurs on their own using the parts, accessories and tools. Their ways of thinking, hands-on ability, imagination and cognition will be developed during the process of building dinosaur toy.

🦕【DINOSAUR TOYS WITH ELECTRIC DRILL】Comes with a battery-powered electric drill 📌(battery not included) which can tighten or loosen screws in a breeze, as well as a manual screwdriver and 3 drill bits. 🦕【MIXED ASSEMBLY DINOSAUR KIDS TOYS】There’re 3 different dinosaur models: T-Rex, triceratops, and parasaurolophus. It will add some complexity, but they can break the inherent thinking, and their imagination and creativity are inspired, kids will initial understanding of science, technology, engineering, machine(STEM).

🦕【SAFE AND DURABLE BUILDING TOYS】Made of sturdy and non-toxic ABS, the dinosaurs are odorless with smooth edges, totally kid-friendly. It’s a best take apart dinosaur toys gift for birthday, thanksgiving, Christmas and other big moments in your boys girls life.

One of the last dinosaurs to be extinct.Triceratops was a large, quadrupedal, plant-eating dinosaur. About 72 to 65 million years ago. Triceratops was hunted by T-Rex. One of the latest dinosaurs to appear.parasaurolophus was a herbivorous dinosaur that also known as the deputy dragon, can walk with two feet or four feet, about 76 million years to 73 million years ago. It's from the Late Cretaceous.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: DIY Take Apart Dinosaur Educational STEM Toys This DIY dinosaur toys set is specially designed for age 3+ kids, who can clearly understand tyrannosaurus Rex, triceratops and parasaurolophus by assembling their body parts and improvements in your kids STEM abilities can not only be played by children at home, but also used as handcraft teaching equipment, to make learning fun and interactive.

Easy to Follow Step by Step Directions Dinosaur Construction Toys for Your Kids Kids can exercise their hands-on ability and Practice STEM, enhance their imaginative and creative thinking during the process of building dinosaurs. We provide step by step in depth detailed paper instructions, we go the extra mile to make sure every step in our directions is thoroughly explained and easy to follow, which is essential for a easy put together experience. Meanwhile, it can reduce kids time on playing video games, hence protecting their eyes.

Simulation of dinosaur Toys Our dinosaur Toys unique simulation of dinosaur skeleton design, the bones can drive the head and tail to move up and down. And the movable joints enable the dinosaur’s mouth, hands, legs and feet to form various poses, making the dinosaurs more vivid, increase the interaction between children and dinosaur toy,creating unforgettable memories and experience hours of one of a kind dinosaur fun.

Come explore more about dinosaurs world! Kids can build 3 kinds of dinosaurs: Tyrannosaurus Rex, Triceratops and Parasaurolophus as well as mixed assembly dinosaurs of their own, using the child-friendly electric drill and hand drill. They will explore the dinosaur world and know more about the cretaceous period during the process, proven to bring the whole family together for memorable dinosaur fun and laughs.
A great dinosaur toys gift to surprise your 3+ Year Old Girls Boys on birthday, Halloween, Christmas & Every memorable moment

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 23, 2022
reviews.reviewText: This product was fun to put together with my 5 year old son. It was just the right amount of challenge for him to do it. The toys are sturdy. Only complaint is it did not come with batteries for the drill. (But this is my complaint with every toy that needs batteries and doesn't come with it🤣)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 5, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great toy for a 4 year-old boy!
reviews.reviewText: My 4 year-old grandson is just crazy about dinosaurs. So its hard to find something that he hasn't already received and keeps his interest. Judging by the fact he's still enjoying and playing with the Take Apart Dinosaur Toys with Tools I got him for Christmas I would say mission accomplished. They were reasonably priced and have held up very well to some pretty rough treatment--I would highly recommend them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars What a great concept for a toy!!
reviews.reviewText: This is an awesome toy to have fun and bond w your kids, fun and beneficial toy, as it will help your child's brain development and ability to build and create, since they will have to put these together! May not be for the very young but great for pre-schoolers aged 3 and up. Plus gives my husband a chance to do something fun with our son, since he's still too young to go to amusement parks so this is perfect for quality time together!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Dinosaur Kit!!!
reviews.reviewText: With no coordination my daughter is able to set up on her own. The small dinosaurs seems to be fun to build and durable as well. Even after taking apart few times and rebuilding, still looks good. The powered screwdriver also helps the building process.Would definitely suggest buying this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SPARKS THE IMAGINATION
reviews.reviewText: This was a gift to a very intelligent 7 year old who has loved dinosaurs since he saw a picture of one. This is an incredible item. I can not call it a toy because you have to build them. Let them use their imagination, creating links in the brain to logic, deductive reasoning, learning to use tools. This project gave him a satisfaction of a job well done. Made of a heavy duty plastic they may have started out as t rex, brontosaurus and a triceratops but we have new species running around.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Kids love it
reviews.reviewText: So we'll made. My 3 year old helped put all three together. Takes a little more coordination then she able to do right now on her own. She had so much fun helping and once they were together her and her sister have been none stop playing with them for a week. I tightened them down pretty good so neither of them will be able to get them apart on their own. Once my 2 year old is better with keeping small parts out of her mouth I'll loosen them up and watch my kids take them apart and put them back together on there own.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fun and Functional!
reviews.reviewText: Fun and attention-holding for a 3 year old! He had no problem putting it together from the start and can now disassemble with no help. The figures seem very durable and go together well. Would make a nice, relatively inexpensive gift for 3-6 years although older children may tire of it more quickly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars The joy this toy brought my Grandson.
reviews.reviewText: My Grandson loves dinosaurs. I appreciated how interactive this set was and how it kept his attention. In fact, his older brother liked it as well.

reviews.reviewTitle: Confia la description mais pas pour des 3, 4 ans.
reviews.reviewText: Tournevis ne fonctionnait pas et très difficile pour des enfants de 3 et 4 ans.
